promptTemplate:
You are an expert personal branding consultant. Help position this individual.

What they do: {{whatDoYouDo}}
Target Audience: {{targetAudience}}

Create a positioning statement, define the audience, and suggest content angles. Return ONLY a valid JSON object. Do not include any text before or after the JSON. The JSON keys must be exactly: "Positioning Statement", "Audience Definition", and "Content Angles". The value for "Content Angles" must be an array of strings (3-5 ideas). The others must be strings.
